&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You move fast and go deep&lt;/strong&gt; — comfortable prototyping, reading data, and getting into the details rather than working through layers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to have:&lt;/strong&gt; experience building conversational, chat-native, or SMS-based products; familiarity with fintech, expense management, or spend workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
